LISTVIEW

static final int LISTVIEW
This represents a list, which is a container for other nodes. This can be used to create a sortable list of nodes, which will usually be a collection of nodes that don't need to be linked with each other (associative links).

See Also:
Constant Field Values

MAPVIEW

static final int MAPVIEW
This represents a map, which is a container for other nodes and links. This can be used to: - create a 'picture'of the relationships between ideas; - group questions and ideas together in meaningful clusters; - create associative links between nodes.
